## How to apply in PR review
- Commits use Conventional Commits; PR covers one logical change.
- PR checklist complete: tests/docs updated; migrations reviewed; changelog updated if public.
- CI must pass all gates; no skipped tests on main.
- pnpm only: `pnpm install`, `pnpm run build`, `pnpm test`; verify TS build locally before push.

