# CI gates (blockers)
- Build, typecheck, lint, test (coverage thresholds), security audit, and size/dep diff.
- No skipped tests in main. Flaky tests are fixed or quarantined with an issue opened.
 - Package manager: pnpm only. Use `pnpm install`, `pnpm run build`, `pnpm test`.
